---
title: Hoisin Pork & Mushrooms with Garlic Rice & Sesame Aioli
description: This dish is an irresistible combination of fresh greens, tasty pork and garlicky rice, with the feel-good factor of cooking a
wholesome meal from scratch. The best part is the sesame aioli to make it super satisfying.

